        "**Feature justification (2-3 sentences):** I chose these features because power prices are linked to daily routines based on human activity and market memory (lag) caused by previous prices, whereas weather captures external shocks in the supply-demand balance. The most predictive variables are hour, which directly impacts the daily rhythm of the price, and price_lag24, which represents market memory and is the strongest cause of autocorrelation.\n",
